es/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n向法庭申請禁令，禁止警察施暴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1312255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1312255</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb96e8b13878fe0e12a58f0fe01b18459311dccf","tid":1314904,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"如果得既公民黨班人點解一直唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係班律師係廢既 一係唔WORK<br />\n推到有專業既答"},{"pid":"b3e8fe1f3e5c106e9af08791601b77bc66cff360","tid":1314904,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1cc27dd2f9109271dad95a4f5bba26bd8df040e","tid":1314904,"uid":78306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"419881173e40362b1545e11eadebcea4ca80c2c4","tid":1314904,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"監警條例亦訂明警務處處長為投訴定案，但無註明涉及投訴警務處處長，例如處長行為失當、作出不合法命令等，條例中並無列明相關機制，亦無任何獨立人仕授權處理涉及處長投訴，即係處長自己查自己。<br />\n<br />\n所有涉及處長投訴，除非成立由法官領導既獨立調查委員會處理，否則監警會係無辦法處理，亦無任何公信力。政府所講所有涉及警務投訴，都可由監警會處理其實並不正確，只要投訴對象係處長，監警會係廢既。<br />\n<br />\n另外民事起訴警方，係並不需要由警方作出調查，咁當然舉證難，入罪難，呢啲就要靠義務律師或者其他有識之仕研究。<br />\n<br />\n等法律JJ研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0150e84f2c04e761cdc504ee48da67dce18c7e","tid":1314904,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2863bd18dda4bb900c4e7a4084f11dacdfe9e03e","tid":1314904,"uid":258409,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"072c6a5ec40beea5792e4b7e4116d13aaf00e305","tid":1314904,"uid":274798,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"其實警例寫左佢地都可以唔跟。姐係依家警權係大過法律。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"警例搵鬼執法咩，法庭落ORDER唔跟就可以同佢玩廢警權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"到時律政師都打埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292148cbc6767d5200bef07b2366011a270ce03e","tid":1314904,"uid":276674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"好似有人做緊司法覆核"},{"pid":"2198a3f6ad9e136639f0e30f5b1eb68277a98f8e","tid":1314904,"uid":92170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"監警會可被起訴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVJuDqG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVJuDqG.png&h=f0dc1cc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ae506f0b125e58dcf7a031492170cee34fd35bb","tid":1314904,"uid":7234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"04b08181e60d2ece177345ea90ac16e9db173749","tid":1314904,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfbee0b6f154193ad15479a9223ff29077dc2cff","tid":1314904,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6862bbd6e016f95765dfa499ac5f3bb89115ff4a","tid":1314904,"uid":229916,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"我個人就咁睇，申請禁制令只要小量人力物力金錢，和理非勇武都唔會反對。<br />\n<br />\n就算申請失敗，都要維持現狀，輸小小錢<br />\n<br />\n但一旦申請成功，即時為全港三萬個警察施加心力壓力。<br />\n<br />\n有人提到執法問題，呢個我個人覺得唔洗擔心，如果一班警察敢集體藐視法庭，起碼上到庭，差佬口供要打折。<br />\n<br />\n最後如果有熟法律的巴打需要資金申請禁制令，如果係一萬幾千細數可以pm 我，我可以比曬。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n點解完全無法律人士做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:58:10.000Z","msg":"推到有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d50bfdfda92a534fbd75a14046685688a3391a","tid":1314904,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b49cc9a6a989cbda460bc11a6b8a3780586d3c68","tid":1314904,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b26ff2e9a94d3964e7cda19ae89a35bd8ab709","tid":1314904,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80afd3d8e6c379d717f56d069263248e464ce98b","tid":1314904,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"陳伯咪申請左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"絕食果個陳伯612後已經做左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"thanks 巴打，有人做就好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:02:52.000Z","msg":"陳佰係入稟法庭，要求推翻警務處批准「速龍小隊」制服不顯示編號做法咋&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/article/七旬陳伯絕食近120小時%E3%80%80「為青年人做啲嘢，我覺得好榮幸」-WrRyGv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Farticle%2F%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E9%99%B3%E4%BC%AF%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E8%BF%91120%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%25E3%2580%2580%E3%80%8C%E7%82%BA%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%9A%E5%95%B2%E5%98%A2%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD%E6%A6%AE%E5%B9%B8%E3%80%8D-WrRyGv&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPalKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=b711be0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/article/七旬陳伯絕食近120小時%E3%80%80「為青年人做啲嘢，我覺得好榮幸」-WrRyGv</a>"},{"pid":"4046907a9a7bc369d6937b9abbc4a73d5a57fc5b","tid":1314904,"uid":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"419881173e40362b1545e11eadebcea4ca80c2c4","tid":1314904,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"監警條例亦訂明警務處處長為投訴定案，但無註明涉及投訴警務處處長，例如處長行為失當、作出不合法命令等，條例中並無列明相關機制，亦無任何獨立人仕授權處理涉及處長投訴，即係處長自己查自己。<br />\n<br />\n所有涉及處長投訴，除非成立由法官領導既獨立調查委員會處理，否則監警會係無辦法處理，亦無任何公信力。政府所講所有涉及警務投訴，都可由監警會處理其實並不正確，只要投訴對象係處長，監警會係廢既。<br />\n<br />\n另外民事起訴警方，係並不需要由警方作出調查，咁當然舉證難，入罪難，呢啲就要靠義務律師或者其他有識之仕研究。<br />\n<br />\n等法律JJ研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"違反禁制令係藐視法庭，係民事，民事舉證簡單好多，警棍扑頭，就算冇片，只要個官信你，都可以入佢！但前題個禁制令要有人搞同個官批&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nBalance of probabilities&nbsp;(standard for adducing evidence in civil litigations) /&nbsp;可能性的權衡&nbsp;(民事訴訟之舉證準則)<br />\n<br />\n「取決於某項事情是否很可能發生過或出現過，但不需要百分百肯定才作出判斷。<br />\nDecision is made according to the likelihood or probability of the existence of an event. A 100% certainty is not required.」"},{"pid":"538a28cb4e6885f07d8e98b1fb348ce5e8d2b390","tid":1314904,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"你意思係強制令。<br />\n<br />\n如果你個人受到實際傷害或損失，可以用司法覆核既方式，以警隊違反司法程序為理由，申請強制令。<br />\n<br />\n但冇案例，好多不確定因素。<br />\n<br />\n利申：半桶水，參考 only"},{"pid":"fec0b941be38fbf2d707219d309ab075378bbe54","tid":1314904,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"538a28cb4e6885f07d8e98b1fb348ce5e8d2b390","tid":1314904,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"你意思係強制令。<br />\n<br />\n如果你個人受到實際傷害或損失，可以用司法覆核既方式，以警隊違反司法程序為理由，申請強制令。<br />\n<br />\n但冇案例，好多不確定因素。<br />\n<br />\n利申：半桶水，參考 only"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:33:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會拖到記協落水？有過幾次係記者被無證狗打傷"},{"pid":"6e2dffff33544bb9584181f5214bef95be4100eb","tid":1314904,"uid":203933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:35:15.000Z","msg":"推到"},{"pid":"70c08e0f423c85e5c956a441f7f624efdbc053a6","tid":1314904,"uid":203933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"5773d65df1e6090ec01d1911bfabd09326dd8739","tid":1314904,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:39:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日又要佔領輿論，港台商台火力全開</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n0800-1000 香港電台第一台<br />\n千禧年代 / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n1700-1800 香港電台第一台<br />\n自由風自由Phone / Phone i